author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of The Staves, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The UBS Forum at Minnesota Public Radio back in 2016.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Outlaw
00:03:14 Sleeping In A Car
00:07:21 Roses
00:11:33 Damn It All

Musicians
Camilla Staveley-Taylor — vocals, guitar, ukelele
Emily Staveley-Taylor — vocals, synth, percussion
Jessica Steveley-Taylor — vocals, guitar, keyboard
Dave Power — drums

Credits
Engineer – Michael DeMark, Erik Stromstad, Andrew Broussard and Brandon Eich
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Visuals  – Nate Ryan, Leah Garaas
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
